                  "jest.runAllTimers() is simpler for isolated tests; jest.advanceTimersByTime() is more precise for testing time-dependent behavior.",
                  "Modern timers (advanceTimers: true) enable advancing Promise-based timers like async/await code.",
                  "jest.clearAllTimers() clears pending timers; jest.getTimerCount() shows how many timers are pending."
